R.A. Fishers famous data on sepal length of a species of Iris Setosa

Data for Exercises 1.15 and 5.19

Format

a numeric vector

a numeric vector

a numeric vector
petalW1
a numeric vector

a numeric vector
sepalW2
a numeric vector
petalL2
a numeric vector
peatalW2
a numeric vector
sepalL3
a numeric vector
sepalW3
a numeric vector
petalL3
a numeric vector
petalW3
a numeric vector
sepalL
a numeric vector
sample
a numeric vector
